        ],
        "summary": "Initiate an international transfer",
        "description": "This endpoint allows users to send funds to international accounts. It requires necessary transfer details such as recipient information, amount, and currency type. Upon successful execution, an acknowledgement of the transaction is returned, allowing for tracking and confirmation of the transfer.",
